Interface QueryResultBinding

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
QueryResultBindingImpl
public interface QueryResultBinding
extends java.lang.Cloneable

Results of query execution. A mapping from variable names to values, which are ATermAppl objects that represent the URI for individuals and the value of literal in the form literal(value, lang, datatypeURI) for data values
